headline: Franklin Templeton celebrates 35th anniversary in Singapore
summary: Franklin Templeton, one of the world's largest global asset managers, is celebrating 35 years of serving clients in Singapore, highlighting its long-standing commitment to delivering world class investment solutions in the country.
